 <text>
  <front>
   <head>To the Same.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">TO ease my troubled mind of anxious care,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Last night the secret casket I explor'd;</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Where all the letters of my absent fair,</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">(His richest treasure) careful Love had stor'd:</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">In ev'ry word a magic spell I found</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Of pow'r to charm each busy thought to rest,</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Though ev'ry word increas'd the tender wound</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Of fond desire still throbbing in my breast.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">So to his hoarded gold the miser steals,</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">And loses ev'ry sorrow at the sight;</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Yet wishes still for more, nor ever feels</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Entire contentment, or secure delight.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="4" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="13" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Ah! should I lose thee, my too lovely maid,</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Cou'dst thou forget thy heart was ever mine,</l>
     <l n="15" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Fear not thy letters shou'd the change upbraid:</l>
     <l n="16" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">My hand each dear memorial shall resign:</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="5" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="17" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Not one kind word shall in my pow'r remain</l>
     <l n="18" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">A painful witness of reproach to thee;</l>
     <l n="19" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">And lest my heart shou'd still their sense retain,</l>
     <l n="20" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">My heart shall break, to leave thee wholly free.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
